    "date": "2024-09-27T15:11:19Z",
    "text": "Renewable Chemicals Act of 2024\n\nThis bill allows a new tax credit for the production of renewable chemicals. Specifically, it allows a credit for u p to 15% of the sales price of each pound of a renewable chemical. A renewable chemical is any chemical that is produced in the United States from renewable biomass and is not less than 95% biobased content.\u00a0\n\nThe bill also allows a 30% tax credit for investment in renewable chemical production facilities.\u00a0"
